short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Make Google Great Again: De-enshittification of Google search.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A simple Chrome extension which redirects all plain searches to the Web tab, which doesn't have all the AI slop and suggested searches and everything else which makes good, simple results harder to find.
